headline: Housing market deals emerge as builder inventory hits 2009 levels
summary: The number of unsold, completed new single-family homes in May 2025 hit the highest level since summer 2009—spurring bigger builder incentives and deals.

headline: KBW Lowers Lennar Price Target, Cites Margin Pressure and Rising Expenses
summary: Lennar Corporation (NYSE:LEN) ranks among the best cyclical stocks to buy now.
